description: This file defines mock API handlers for a gym management frontend, using msw to mock endpoints for authentication, members, trainers, classes, bookings, programs, and payments. It includes seed data imports, in-memory data manipulation, and handler functions for CRUD operations and other API interactions.

methods.name: buildHandlers()
methods.description: Builds and returns an array of mocked API handlers for the gym management system, maintaining in-memory seed data, and includes handlers for auth, members, trainers, classes, bookings, programs, and payments.
